export function FitCss () {
        const converted = {
            "*": { margin: "0", padding: "0", boxSizing: "border-box" },
            "@font-face": {
              fontFamily: '"Iwona"',
              src: 'url("./IwonaMedium-Regular.ttf")'
            },
            ".hamburger-menu": { height: "0" },
            "#menu__toggle": { display: "none" },
            "#menu__toggle:checked + .menu__btn > span": { transform: "rotate(45deg)" },
            "#menu__toggle:checked + .menu__btn > span::before": {
              top: "0",
              transform: "rotate(0deg)"
            },
            "#menu__toggle:checked + .menu__btn > span::after": {
              top: "0",
              transform: "rotate(90deg)"
            },
            "#menu__toggle:checked ~ .menu__box": { left: "0 !important" },
            ".menu__btn": {
              position: "fixed",
              top: "50px",
              left: "20px",
              width: "26px",
              height: "26px",
              cursor: "pointer",
              zIndex: 1
            },
            ".menu__btn > span,\n  .menu__btn > span::before,\n  .menu__btn > span::after": {
              display: "block",
              position: "absolute",
              width: "100%",
              height: "2px",
              backgroundColor: "#616161",
              transitionDuration: ".25s"
            },
            ".menu__btn > span::before": { content: "''", top: "-8px" },
            ".menu__btn > span::after": { content: "''", top: "8px" },
            ".menu__box": {
              display: "block",
              position: "fixed",
              top: "0",
              left: "-100%",
              width: "300px",
              height: "100%",
              margin: "0",
              padding: "80px 0",
              listStyle: "none",
              backgroundColor: "#ded8ce9c",
              boxShadow: "2px 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, .4)",
              transitionDuration: ".25s"
            },
            ".menu__item": {
              display: "block",
              padding: "12px 24px",
              color: "#333",
              fontFamily: "'Iwona', sans-serif",
              fontSize: "20px",
              fontWeight: 600,
              textDecoration: "none",
              transitionDuration: ".25s"
            },
            ".menu__item:hover": { backgroundColor: "#CFD8DC" },
            body: { margin: "0", fontFamily: "Iwona, sans-serif" },
            ".parallax-container": {
              display: "flex",
              minHeight: "100vh",
              flexDirection: "column",
              alignItems: "center",
              justifyContent: "center",
              backgroundAttachment: "fixed",
              backgroundImage:
                "url(https://vsegda-pomnim.com/uploads/posts/2022-04/1651044559_1-vsegda-pomnim-com-p-bezhevoe-more-foto-4.jpg)",
              backgroundPosition: "center",
              backgroundSize: "cover",
              color: "rgb(85, 83, 83)",
              rowGap: "4rem",
              textAlign: "center"
            },
            ".buffer1": {
              width: "100%",
              minHeight: "35vh",
              backgroundColor: "rgb(38, 37, 37)"
            },
            ".parallax-container2": {
              flexDirection: "row",
              flexWrap: "wrap",
              padding: "6rem 0",
              backgroundImage:
                "url(https://priroda.club/uploads/posts/2022-12/1670448321_priroda-club-p-bezhevoe-more-krasivo-foto-33.jpg)",
              gap: "1.6em"
            },
            h1: { fontSize: "4rem", fontWeight: 700, color: "rgb(38, 37, 37)" },
            p: {
              maxWidth: "52ch",
              padding: "1em",
              lineHeight: 1.5,
              color: "rgb(38, 37, 37)"
            },
            ".buffer1 p": {
              color: "#CFD8DC",
              maxWidth: "52ch",
              padding: "3em",
              lineHeight: 1.5,
              marginLeft: "auto",
              marginRight: "auto",
              fontSize: "30px",
              textAlign: "center",
              fontStyle: "italic"
            },
            b: { maxWidth: "52ch", fontSize: "1.5rem", color: "rgb(38, 37, 37)" },
            ".card a": {
              display: "inline-block",
              borderRadius: "0.3em",
              color: "rgb(38, 37, 37)",
              fontSize: "0.875rem",
              fontWeight: 700,
              letterSpacing: "0.5px",
              textDecoration: "none",
              textTransform: "uppercase"
            },
            ".card a:hover": { color: "#ddca85" },
            h3: { marginTop: "1em", fontSize: "1.6rem", fontWeight: 700 },
            ".card": {
              display: "flex",
              maxWidth: "320px",
              flexDirection: "column",
              alignItems: "center",
              paddingBottom: "1rem",
              borderRadius: "0.5em",
              backgroundColor: "white",
              boxShadow: "0 29px 38px -15px rgb(0 0 0 / 43%)"
            },
            ".card-img": {
              width: "100%",
              height: "200px",
              borderRadius: "0.3em",
              backgroundPosition: "center",
              backgroundSize: "cover"
            },
            ".card:nth-of-type(1) .card-img": {
              backgroundImage:
                "url(https://pro-dachnikov.com/uploads/posts/2021-10/1633568218_42-p-fotostudiya-domgrafa-pyatigorsk-foto-44.jpg)"
            },
            ".card:nth-of-type(2) .card-img": {
              backgroundImage:
                "url(https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-altay/216588/2a0000015b17da23fa2b741bef4bf2cc449e/XXL)"
            },
            ".card:nth-of-type(3) .card-img": {
              backgroundImage:
                "url(https://sanada.club/uploads/posts/2021-03/1615557416_51-p-studii-dlya-fotosessii-v-moskve-51.jpg)"
            },
            ".container": { maxWidth: "1170px", margin: "auto" },
            ul: { listStyle: "none" },
            ".footer": { backgroundColor: "#24262b", padding: "20px 0" },
            ".footer .row": {
              display: "flex",
              flexWrap: "wrap",
              justifyContent: "center"
            },
            ".footer-col": { width: "25%", padding: "0 15px" },
            ".footer-col h4": {
              fontSize: "25px",
              color: "#ffffff",
              textTransform: "capitalize",
              marginBottom: "35px",
              fontWeight: 500,
              position: "relative"
            },
            ".footer-col h4::before": {
              content: "''",
              position: "absolute",
              left: "0",
              bottom: "-10px",
              backgroundColor: "#e91e63",
              height: "2px",
              boxSizing: "border-box",
              width: "50px"
            },
            ".footer-col ul li:not(:last-child)": { marginBottom: "10px" },
            ".footer-col ul li a": {
              fontSize: "25px",
              textTransform: "capitalize",
              color: ["#ffffff", "#bbbbbb"],
              textDecoration: "none",
              fontWeight: 300,
              display: "block",
              transition: "all 0.3s ease"
            },
            ".footer-col ul li a:hover": { color: "#ffffff", paddingLeft: "8px" },
            ".footer-col .social-links": {
              display: "flex",
              flexDirection: "column",
              gap: "10px"
            },
            ".footer-col .social-links a": {
              display: "block",
              backgroundColor: "rgba(255,255,255,0.2)",
              color: "#ffffff",
              transition: "all 0.5s ease",
              fontSize: "30px",
              width: "57.6px",
              padding: "8px",
              borderRadius: "100%",
              textAlign: "center"
            },
            ".footer-col .social-links a:hover": {
              color: "#24262b",
              backgroundColor: "#ffffff"
            },
            "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
              ".footer-col": { width: "50%", marginBottom: "30px" }
            },
            "@media (max-width: 574px)": { ".footer-col": { width: "100%" } }
          }
    
}
